Lillian Kemble-Cooper https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lillian_Kemble-Cooper 0 Lillian Kemble-Cooper (March 21, 1892 in London, England – May 4, 1977 in Los Angeles, USA) was an English-born actress, who after emigrating to the US had a successful career on Broadway and in Hollywood film.
